name: Not rewind time
description:
Are you tired of the same lame utub rewind every year? Now it's your chance to prove you are the ultimate king of dislikes! Challenge your friends and see who can create more accounts and dislike the video as much as possible in 3 minutes only.  Not Rewind Time is a  frenzy and chaotic game  that will put you to the test, good memory and good typing skills will be mandatory to excel in this game.

Music and SFX: Gonzalo Cabeza, Dante Cuffia.

2D Artist: Ayelen Galvan.

Programmers: Juan Pablo Bortol, Fabrizzio Morandi.
